description:
IF knows that the sun is the perfect source for Vitamin D! Grab the IF Swimsuit Outfit and duke it out against any 2D enemy!

Note: Players can access the IF Swimsuit Outfit by going to the Menu and scrolling to the Equipment section. The IF Swimsuit Outfit is purely cosmetic and is visible during battle, cut scenes, and exploration segments with Neptune. Mix-n-match with the animal sets for fun!
name: IF Swimsuit Outfit
